### **3. 34_LogPatternSniffer**  
**Description:**  
Scans system or app logs to identify repeating errors and patterns.

#### **README.md**
```markdown
# LogPatternSniffer - Log Error Analyzer

LogPatternSniffer reads logs and detects repeated error messages or suspicious phrases.

## Features
- Auth log & syslog support  
- Grouped keyword frequency  
- Command line friendly  

## Usage
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/34_LogPatternSniffer.git
cd 34_LogPatternSniffer
python analyze.py /var/log/syslog
